	    boolean isJavadocTag(int type) {
	        switch(type) {
	            case AUTHOR_LITERAL:
	            case DEPRECATED_LITERAL:
	            case EXCEPTION_LITERAL:

	            case RETURN_LITERAL:

	            case SERIAL_DATA_LITERAL:
	            case SINCE_LITERAL:
	            case THROWS_LITERAL:
	            case VERSION_LITERAL:
	            case CUSTOM_NAME:
	                return true;
	            default:
	                return false;
	        }
	    }
